reviews.text: Great Lebanese food and nice ambiance. Definitely recommend this restaurant. Be sure to check out the lounge for the best Shisha in town by far!
Best shisha in Hong Kong and decent Mediterranean food. Worth the price. Most friendly staff in the area!
Very delicious chicken skewers and liver! Good food and friendly service. Love it!
Worth every penny. The shared meat platter is literally heaven for the tastebuds. The whole menu is fantastic and the staff is soo friendly. Highly recommend especially for big groups.
Amazing ! Lebanese food done to perfection ! Great speakeasy , hidden gem !
